^ a b Watts, Alex (May 2, 2010). "Warning As Baby Medicines Are Recalled". Sky News. Archived from the original on May 4, 2010. Retrieved May 3, 2010. 
^ a b c d e f g h i j Layton, Lyndsey (May 2, 2010). "Johnson & Johnson division recalls 43 OTC medicines for infants and children". Washington Post. Retrieved May 3, 2010. 
^ a b c Singer, Natasha (May 1, 2010). "Children's Tylenol and Other Drugs Recalled". The New York Times. Archived from the original on May 4, 2010. Retrieved May 3, 2010. 
^ a b c d "Panel Investigates J.&J. Recalls". New York Times. Reuters. May 6, 2010. Retrieved May 7, 2010. 
